# Keep secrets and local cruft out of the build context / image
**/node_modules
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/dist
**/.vite
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# VCS / IDE / docs
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
.agents
.claude
**/*.md

# Tests & reports (not needed at runtime)
e2e
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/.auth

# Misc
*.png
docker-compose.yml
